The '''AV-21''' was a type of vehicle.<ref name="Solo" /> In [[10 BBY]],<ref name="Official Guide">''[[Solo: A Star Wars Story The Official Guide]]''</ref> the [[Corellian]] [[Han Solo]] told [[Tobias Beckett]] that he had been [[Thief|stealing]] AV-21s since he was ten [[Standard year|years]] old.<ref name="Solo" />

{{Veh-stub}}

==Behind the scenes==
In the ''[[Star Wars]]'' [[canon]], AV-21s were first identified in the [[2018]] [[Star Wars Anthology Series|''Anthology'']] film ''[[Solo: A Star Wars Story]]''.<ref name="Solo" /> In the [[Star Wars Legends|''Star Wars'' Legends]] continuity, AV-21s were a type of [[Landspeeder/Legends|landspeeder]] created for the [[2003]] [[Star Wars video games|video game]] [[Star Wars Galaxies|''Star Wars Galaxies: An Empire Divided'']].<ref name="Galaxies">{{GalaxiesAED}}</ref>

